                  </persName>
            . I was in the King's Head public-house. Whittem gave the prisoner in charge, and desired me to search him, and I found ten pieces of ribbon on him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave myself to the mercy of the court.</p>
